{"tid":529682,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新民黨陳家珮正式宣布參選立法會港島區補選","createTime":"2018-01-15T04:23:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-16T03:04:57.000Z","uid":20816,"like":1,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"1d4035b27d15cccbd9b66b63b59904d8320f6650","tid":529682,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T04:23:14.000Z","msg":"source:有線新聞"},{"pid":"2346871356c91c6710292b7e6eb6cdd851a726dd","tid":529682,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T04:32:05.000Z","msg":"陳家珮宣布代表建制參加港島補選 2018/01/15 12:04<br />\n立法會補選明天開始接受提名，新民黨成員陳家珮宣布代表建制派參加香港島補選。 <br />\n<br />\n陳家珮在新民黨主席葉劉淑儀陪同下，宣布參選。她以「捍衛法治、回歸理性」作為競選口號。她表示已經獲得民建聯和工聯會全力支持她取得席位。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n除了陳家珮，香港眾志常委周庭早前已表明將會代表泛民，參與香港島補選。社民連前成員任亮憲日前亦表態，有意出選香港島。<br />\n<a href=\"http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/519716/即時新聞/陳家珮宣布代表建制參加港島補選\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F519716%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F%E9%99%B3%E5%AE%B6%E7%8F%AE%E5%AE%A3%E5%B8%83%E4%BB%A3%E8%A1%A8%E5%BB%BA%E5%88%B6%E5%8F%83%E5%8A%A0%E6%B8%AF%E5%B3%B6%E8%A3%9C%E9%81%B8&d=28XKaMuCrbGEpBhY%2BSxH1k%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=0ae225d1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F519716%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F%E9%99%B3%E5%AE%B6%E7%8F%AE%E5%AE%A3%E5%B8%83%E4%BB%A3%E8%A1%A8%E5%BB%BA%E5%88%B6%E5%8F%83%E5%8A%A0%E6%B8%AF%E5%B3%B6%E8%A3%9C%E9%81%B8&h=8938d318\" target=\"_blank\">http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/519716/即時新聞/陳家珮宣布代表建制參加港島補選</a>"},{"pid":"bd04e12d95835a1472aab3e7c77757dde8d1fd1e","tid":529682,"uid":50740,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T04:41:35.000Z","msg":"周庭贏晒"},{"pid":"8fe8a4bc886c8366f1c6da8b340c62b38d5ee222","tid":529682,"uid":42804,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bd04e12d95835a1472aab3e7c77757dde8d1fd1e","tid":529682,"uid":507